<h1 class="mb-4"><i class="bi bi-key"></i> 更改密码</h1>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <div class="card shadow-sm">
      <div class="card-body">
        <form action="/users/change-password" method="POST">
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="currentPassword" class="form-label">当前密码</label>
            <input
              type="password"
              id="currentPassword"
              name="currentPassword"
              class="form-control"
              placeholder="请输入当前密码"
              required
            />
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="newPassword" class="form-label">新密码</label>
            <input
              type="password"
              id="newPassword"
              name="newPassword"
              class="form-control"
              placeholder="请输入新密码（至少6位）"
              required
            />
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="confirmPassword" class="form-label">确认新密码</label>
            <input
              type="password"
              id="confirmPassword"
              name="confirmPassword"
              class="form-control"
              placeholder="请再次输入新密码"
              required
            />
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary me-2">更改密码</button>
            <a href="/users/profile" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">返回个人资料</a>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card shadow-sm">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h4 class="card-title">密码要求</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>密码长度至少6个字符</li>
          <li>建议使用字母、数字和符号的组合</li>
          <li>请勿使用与旧密码相同的密码</li>
          <li>请勿使用容易被猜到的密码</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>